>>> Start with FlightBookingSystem class
We need list of users and airport

>> Define Users
Users are multiple entities here.
User can be a customer who is using the application
User can be an employee with the airport
User can be a Pilot/Crew

>> Define Airport

Each airport will have list of Flights (class Flight)
Each Flight will have a list of schedules (class FlightSchedule)
Each schedule will have a list of seat to book (Class FlightSeat)

>> User can create an Itinerary after searching the flight

An Itinerary can have multiple FlightReservations
Each FlightReservation, have one start and end airport location, fare details,
seats booked for cPassengers.